    • Rectangle

      public Rectangle(Point[] inShape, Point inPosition, double inRotation)
      Constructs a rectangle with the specified shape, position, and rotation. Calls Element class constructor to create rectangle object.
      Parameters:
      inShape - The shape of the spaceship.
      inPosition - The position of the spaceship.
      inRotation - The rotation of the spaceship.
